{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Provide a second set of grants and funding to businesses due to lockdown.",
        "additional_details": "Businesses have had a difficult time during the pandemic, and despite generous funding during the first lockdown, a lot of time has passed. Many businesses are on the brink and with the new lockdown the funding could be the difference between their survival or otherwise.",
        "background": "Due to the January 2021 lockdown, especially with schools being closed, all businesses are going to be impacted to a similar level as they were back in March 2020. \r\n\r\nTherefore the same level of support should be made available to all businesses again, regardless of if they received prior funding.",
